Motormaster looked down at Symphony in discust. Megatron must see 
something he didnt. He shifted his hands, so he was holding him with 
one hand, and smacked him in the head with his other. "Dont tempt me 
to drop you" he said, not quite sure what that noise was that was 
somewhere around. He was nearing the other Stunticons.

"Yeah, dont tempt him, he will" laughed Wildrider Cruely. They were 
nearing South Africa.
